      • Port

        public Port(java.lang.String namePort,
            java.lang.String nationPort,
            double population,
            boolean passRequire,
            double fee,
            boolean isUsed)
        Constructor method for the port. Ensure the ports by their information(name, nation, population, whether require the passport, fee and whether used before) saved in the data base.
        参数:
        namePort - the name of the port
        nationPort - the nation of the port
        population - the population of the port
        passRequire - whether the port requires the passport
        fee - the fee of the port
        isUsed - whether the port is used before
